<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>分类您的商品</title>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/favicon.ico">
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/favicon.ico">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge,chrome=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/base.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/creat_new_product.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="sc-content-container">
            <div id="page_header" class="a-container">
                <h1 class="a-color-state">
                    创建新商品：分类
                </h1>
                <span>要开始创建详情页面，首先请分类您的商品。<a href="###">了解更多详情</a></span>
            </div>
            <div  id="search_header" class="a-container">
                <div class="a-span6">
                    <div class="a-box-group">
                        <div class="search_box">
                            <h3>搜索您商品的分类</h3>
                            <div class="category_search_form">
                                <input type="text" id="category_search" placeholder="例如：mp3 播放器，棒球手套，DVD，吉他等"/>
                                <button class="button button-primary" id="category_search_button" type=button>搜索分类</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="find_it_on_amazon_box">
                            <h4 class="find_on_amazon">
                                <strong>您所添加的商品已可在亚马逊上找到：</strong>
                                <button  class="button button-inner" id="find_it_on_amazon" onclick="window.location.href= 'add_product.html';return false">在亚马逊上查找</button>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="category_picker" class="a-container">
                <div class="a-box-group">
                    <div class="careful">
                        <span>
                            注意：如果您的产品类别未在下方列出，可能是因为需要批准、受到限制或您的申请正在审查中。
                        </span>
                        <br />
                        <span>
                            <a href="###">了解更多</a>或查看您的<a href="###">销售应用程序状态</a>。
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="browse_category_picker" class="box-inner">
                        <h4 class="bread_crumbs"><a href="###">所有商品分类</a></h4>
                        <div id="browse_category_carousel" class="clear_both">
                            <!-- addClass  pagination_inner  removeClass button-disabled-->
                            <span id='backward_button' class='pagination button-disabled'>
                                <i class='a-icon a-icon-previous'></i>
                            </span>
                            <div id='category_browse' class="clear_both"></div>
                            <span id='forward_button' class='pagination button-disabled'>
                                <i class='a-icon a-icon-next'></i>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cancel_box">
                        <button class="button button-text" id="cancel" onclick="javascript:history.go(-1)">取消</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/public.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/webjs/creat_new_product.js"></script>
</html>